  "detailed_description": "<strong>MPAliens</strong> - 2D Arena Platformer. It's a local party game with intense PVP matches, hardest COOP missions and different Bosses on different maps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/2555c9b028944c415eb9de9f2c63c9ba.poster.avif?t=1564227804\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/2555c9b028944c415eb9de9f2c63c9ba.webm?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/2555c9b028944c415eb9de9f2c63c9ba.mp4?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features :</strong><br>- 17 Weapons<br>- 6 Maps<br>- PvP<br>- COOP!<br>- BOSSES!<br>- Different platformer mechanics<br>- Great  chiptune by RWG<br><br><strong>Simple, understandable movement </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/f073b3bb51b3915d0d9d610e6485625a.poster.avif?t=1564227804\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/f073b3bb51b3915d0d9d610e6485625a.webm?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/f073b3bb51b3915d0d9d610e6485625a.mp4?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Slide Shot</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/d8244918a8096fcaa553442b8dec2a49.poster.avif?t=1564227804\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/d8244918a8096fcaa553442b8dec2a49.webm?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/d8244918a8096fcaa553442b8dec2a49.mp4?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Teleport Shot</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/d60d16329c558a0647ec7c0b3a00a7e7.poster.avif?t=1564227804\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/d60d16329c558a0647ec7c0b3a00a7e7.webm?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/d60d16329c558a0647ec7c0b3a00a7e7.mp4?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Traps and special mechanics</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/1d473678a2b4ed5c51ed2d4cf6cbec91.poster.avif?t=1564227804\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/1d473678a2b4ed5c51ed2d4cf6cbec91.webm?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/1d473678a2b4ed5c51ed2d4cf6cbec91.mp4?t=1564227804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068110/extras/3f447c59ef4582dbebe3f2029c957578.poster.avif?t=1564227804\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st